This is so extensions can check platform types to either only load on certain platforms or do certain things depending on platform.

EG: Disabling the extension if not running on Geyser Standalone
```java
@Subscribe
public void onPreInitialize(GeyserPreInitializeEvent event) {
    if (this.geyserApi().platformType() != PlatformType.STANDALONE) {
        this.logger().severe("GeyserConnect is only supported on standalone Geyser instances!");
        this.disable();
    }
}
```

