Also renamed TranslatorsInit to Translators, since that makes more sense.

usage
```java
@Translator(packet = SomePacket.class)
public class SomeTranslator extends PacketTranslator<SomePacket> {
    // ...
}
```

Register a packet translator like this:
```java
@Translator(packet = SomePacket.class)
public class SomeTranslator extends PacketTranslator<SomePacket> {
    // ...
}
```

Also includes the RELEASE flag, to warn users that the version of Geyser they're about to use isn't production ready.
